  *** Be sure to use the -oA flag as a best practice. This will ensure that we have scan results in several formats for logging purposes and formats that can be manipulated and fed into other tools.

Sample steps:
  sudo nmap --open -oA inlanefreight_ept_tcp_1k.txt -iL scope.txt (查1000个常用ports)
  sudo nmap --open -p- -sV -oA inlanefreight_ept_tcp_all_svc -iL scope (查1000的版本)
  sudo nmap --open -p- -A -oA inlanefreight_ept_tcp_all_svc -iL scope  (查全ports的版本)


